# Governance

- [`authority.md`](authority.md) separates capability from authorization.
- [`automation-register.json`](automation-register.json) admits only settled,
  observable work with authority, durable state, proof, and escalation.
- [`feedback-controls.json`](feedback-controls.json) routes repeated findings to
  the earliest durable owner and records retirement of weaker reminders.
- [`epochs/`](epochs/) requalifies the harness when worker, host, tools, or
  runtime changes.
- [`effectiveness/`](effectiveness/) measures accepted outcomes and human
  attention, not activity volume.
